core:processNote.core:description:
This process is the main process that manages the SingleThreadedConfigurableQueueConsumer.
This is a replacement for the old ConfigurableQueueConsumerService process that uses the new QueueConsumer implementation.
It does not support retry messages (currently)

core:param.value: Service definition must be an instance of IMultiThreadedQueueConsumerServiceDefinition.
core:param.name: enactor.coreUI.LogMessage
